the culmination of materialism.

00:05:43.640 --> 00:05:45.320 align:middle line:84%
See, materialism
really didn't get

00:05:45.320 --> 00:05:47.890 align:middle line:84%
going-- it started, roughly,
around the Enlightenment,

00:05:47.890 --> 00:05:49.590 align:middle line:90%
like the 1600s, right?

00:05:49.590 --> 00:05:50.482 align:middle line:90%
And it got going.

00:05:50.482 --> 00:05:51.440 align:middle line:90%
It got going and going.

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:54.230 align:middle line:84%
And it peaked in the late 1800s,
to the point where they wanted

00:05:54.230 --> 00:05:55.640 align:middle line:90%
to close the patent office.

00:05:55.640 --> 00:05:57.015 align:middle line:84%
They thought they
knew everything

00:05:57.015 --> 00:05:58.940 align:middle line:84%
about every invention
that's ever been done.

00:05:58.940 --> 00:06:00.440 align:middle line:84%
All physics has already
been discovered.

00:06:00.440 --> 00:06:02.731 align:middle line:84%
And then, lo and behold, they
discover quantum physics.

00:06:02.731 --> 00:06:04.980 align:middle line:84%
But medicine was
birthed at the time

00:06:04.980 --> 00:06:06.850 align:middle line:90%
of this peak of materialism.

00:06:06.850 --> 00:06:08.780 align:middle line:84%
And in fairness, it
was pretty amazing

00:06:08.780 --> 00:06:10.090 align:middle line:90%
compared to the Middle Ages.

00:06:10.090 --> 00:06:11.010 align:middle line:90%
Materialism gave us electricity.

00:06:11.010 --> 00:06:12.051 align:middle line:90%
It gave us the telegraph.

00:06:12.051 --> 00:06:13.461 align:middle line:84%
It gave us, you
know, anesthesia.

00:06:13.461 --> 00:06:15.710 align:middle line:84%
It gave us some wonderful
things compared to what life

00:06:15.710 --> 00:06:17.120 align:middle line:90%
was like in the Middle Ages.

00:06:17.120 --> 00:06:20.180 align:middle line:90%
But that was the end of it.

00:06:20.180 --> 00:06:21.500 align:middle line:90%
It did what it could do.

00:06:21.500 --> 00:06:23.390 align:middle line:84%
And then, we moved
on, scientifically,

00:06:23.390 --> 00:06:24.560 align:middle line:90%
to the quantum age.

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:26.060 align:middle line:90%
Now, the quantum age is not--

00:06:26.060 --> 00:06:28.460 align:middle line:84%
it sounds kind of airy-fairy
