00:06:28.460 --> 00:06:29.260 align:middle line:90%
relevant.

00:06:29.260 --> 00:06:31.197 align:middle line:84%
But our CDs work
with quantum physics.

00:06:31.197 --> 00:06:32.780 align:middle line:84%
Our iPhones work
with quantum physics.

00:06:32.780 --> 00:06:34.280 align:middle line:84%
We interact with
quantum physics,

00:06:34.280 --> 00:06:36.696 align:middle line:84%
the verities of quantum physics
every minute of our lives.

00:06:36.696 --> 00:06:40.317 align:middle line:84%
