And this is a great
battle that exists

00:07:04.820 --> 00:07:07.880 align:middle line:84%
at all times, institutions
versus the individual.

00:07:07.880 --> 00:07:10.340 align:middle line:84%
The institutions of government,
the institutions of law,

00:07:10.340 --> 00:07:13.430 align:middle line:84%
the institutions of banking,
the institutions of medicine

00:07:13.430 --> 00:07:15.590 align:middle line:84%
are all there to
perpetuate themselves.

00:07:15.590 --> 00:07:18.290 align:middle line:84%
And the individual is
just there as a resource

00:07:18.290 --> 00:07:19.610 align:middle line:90%
for the institution.

00:07:19.610 --> 00:07:21.620 align:middle line:84%
And this happens with
all institutions.

00:07:21.620 --> 00:07:25.640 align:middle line:84%
And an end result is that you
have an institution of medicine

00:07:25.640 --> 00:07:27.470 align:middle line:84%
that prides itself
on how wonderful it

