00:33:33.220 --> 00:33:33.580 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: But then--

00:33:33.580 --> 00:33:34.570 align:middle line:90%
>>FUCHS: Is that a disease?

00:33:34.570 --> 00:33:35.290 align:middle line:90%
