is breaking down.

00:33:36.790 --> 00:33:38.719 align:middle line:84%
There's not 12,800
different diseases.

00:33:38.719 --> 00:33:40.010 align:middle line:90%
The body is just breaking down.

00:33:40.010 --> 00:33:41.290 align:middle line:90%
There's only one disease.

00:33:41.290 --> 00:33:45.020 align:middle line:84%
MBFA disease, my body is
falling apart disease.

00:33:45.020 --> 00:33:46.660 align:middle line:84%
That's the only
disease there is.

00:33:46.660 --> 00:33:48.162 align:middle line:84%
Your body's is
just deteriorating,

00:33:48.162 --> 00:33:50.620 align:middle line:84%
whether it's in your muscles
