00:33:53.260 --> 00:33:54.520 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't matter.

00:33:54.520 --> 00:33:57.130 align:middle line:84%
The body is breaking
down as a system.

00:33:57.130 --> 00:34:00.730 align:middle line:84%
And when the body breaks down
as a system, all you need to do

00:34:00.730 --> 00:34:02.830 align:middle line:84%
