A bone cell is not
condemned to be a bone cell.

00:36:16.310 --> 00:36:18.980 align:middle line:84%
It can be a skin cell if it
has the right environment.

00:36:18.980 --> 00:36:21.739 align:middle line:84%
The environment tells
the genes what to do.

00:36:21.739 --> 00:36:23.155 align:middle line:84%
