Take a look at this.

00:49:00.860 --> 00:49:02.610 align:middle line:10%
>>FUCHS: One of the
most fundamental ideas

00:49:02.610 --> 00:49:06.090 align:middle line:10%
is the fact that what
you're diagnosed with

00:49:06.090 --> 00:49:11.820 align:middle line:10%
is not the problem in terms of
reversing your health issue.

00:49:11.820 --> 00:49:15.390 align:middle line:10%
Medical diagnoses are
conveniences that doctors

00:49:15.390 --> 00:49:18.440 align:middle line:10%
use to explain symptomology.

00:49:18.440 --> 00:49:23.055 align:middle line:10%
And we get obsessed
with symptomology

00:49:23.055 --> 00:49:26.610 align:middle line:10%
and end up marginalizing or
being dismissive of causes.

00:49:26.610 --> 00:49:28.920 align:middle line:10%
In other words, we have
a pharmaco-medical model

00:49:28.920 --> 00:49:30.540 align:middle line:10%
that treats symptoms
as if they were

00:49:30.540 --> 00:49:33.720 align:middle line:10%
the diseases, that
treats symptoms

00:49:33.720 --> 00:49:36.690 align:middle line:10%
as if those were the problems.

00:49:36.690 --> 00:49:39.390 align:middle line:10%
The symptom may be
problematic in terms

00:49:39.390 --> 00:49:41.280 align:middle line:10%
of how you live your life.

00:49:41.280 --> 00:49:44.400 align:middle line:84%
But as far as reversing
the symptomology,

00:49:44.400 --> 00:49:47.140 align:middle line:90%
your diagnosis doesn't matter.

00:49:47.140 --> 00:49:50.530 align:middle line:84%
The breakdowns in the
body are always generic.

00:49:50.530 --> 00:49:53.130 align:middle line:84%
And whether it shows
up as osteoporosis

00:49:53.130 --> 00:49:56.460 align:middle line:84%
or autoimmune disease or
skin diseases or cancer,

00:49:56.460 --> 00:49:58.770 align:middle line:84%
you're always going
to see the same things

00:49:58.770 --> 00:50:02.910 align:middle line:84%
underneath or behind all
the various symptomologies

00:50:02.910 --> 00:50:05.680 align:middle line:84%
that are associated with
these different diagnoses.

00:50:05.680 --> 00:50:07.860 align:middle line:84%
And if you want to
reverse the disease state,

00:50:07.860 --> 00:50:09.790 align:middle line:84%
it doesn't matter
what the diagnosis is.

00:50:09.790 --> 00:50:12.120 align:middle line:84%
And it doesn't even matter
what the symptomology is.

00:50:12.120 --> 00:50:14.010 align:middle line:90%
What matters is the cause.

00:50:14.010 --> 00:50:18.540 align:middle line:10%
If you have a tree that is
producing rotten fruit or moldy

00:50:18.540 --> 00:50:22.380 align:middle line:10%
leaves, you don't
spray the leaves.

00:50:22.380 --> 00:50:24.540 align:middle line:84%
You don't correct the
problem at the level

00:50:24.540 --> 00:50:25.650 align:middle line:90%
of the fruit or the leaf.

00:50:25.650 --> 00:50:30.280 align:middle line:84%
You correct the problem
at the level of the soil.

00:50:30.280 --> 00:50:32.310 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So if we are
