But it seems that's
the key there,

00:56:03.486 --> 00:56:07.130 align:middle line:84%
is to really understand
the psychological aspects

00:56:07.130 --> 00:56:08.690 align:middle line:90%
of disease and illness.

00:56:08.690 --> 00:56:09.490 align:middle line:90%
>>FUCHS: Yes.

00:56:09.490 --> 00:56:12.630 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And I got to ask
you, why do you do this?

00:56:12.630 --> 00:56:14.287 align:middle line:90%
What is your biggest why?

00:56:14.287 --> 00:56:15.620 align:middle line:90%
>>FUCHS: What is my biggest why?

00:56:15.620 --> 00:56:16.880 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: In all
that you do, yeah.

00:56:16.880 --> 00:56:19.046 align:middle line:84%
>>FUCHS: You know, if you
