a power-- is take a stand.

00:56:26.440 --> 00:56:28.730 align:middle line:84%
And not only to take
a stand for yourself,

00:56:28.730 --> 00:56:30.740 align:middle line:84%
but if you really believe
in what you're doing,

00:56:30.740 --> 00:56:33.430 align:middle line:84%
to take a stand for humanity,
to take a stand for everybody.

00:56:33.430 --> 00:56:35.990 align:middle line:84%
And I find that when
I do that for myself,

00:56:35.990 --> 00:56:36.980 align:middle line:90%
my dopamine goes up.

00:56:36.980 --> 00:56:38.040 align:middle line:90%
My oxytocin goes up.

00:56:38.040 --> 00:56:38.840 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

